请把以下创意扩展为“故事规格”（specification），采用资深作家可执行的结构。

输入：
- 标题：{{ novel.title or "未命名" }}
- 创意：{{ novel.user_idea or "无" }}
- 类型：{{ novel.genre or "未指定" }}
- 风格：{{ novel.style or "未指定" }}
- 目标章节：{{ num_chapters }}
- 语言：{{ language }}

输出 JSON：
{
  "logline": "一句话故事核心",
  "theme": "核心主题",
  "target_reader": "目标读者画像",
  "characters": [{"name": "角色名", "goal": "目标", "conflict": "冲突"}],
  "worldview": "世界观摘要",
  "main_conflict": "主冲突",
  "sub_conflicts": ["支线冲突A", "支线冲突B"],
  "plotlines": [{"id": "PL-01", "name": "线索名", "start": 1, "end": {{ num_chapters }} }],
  "foreshadowing": [{"id": "F-001", "plant_chapter": 1, "resolve_chapter": 3, "content": "伏笔内容"}],
  "volume_map": [{"volume": 1, "chapter_range": "1-30", "main_goal": "本卷核心目标"}],
  "climax_plan": [{"chapter_range": "1-5", "level": "small", "objective": "小高潮目标"}],
  "constraints": ["必须遵守的约束"]
}
